{"tid":565194,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雷神輸掉馬迷兩億！(內含A09😍$400大元)","createTime":"2018-02-18T17:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T07:19:22.000Z","uid":1426,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"24fff544258170dbe40ec1dd9562b5e1f7327502","tid":565194,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:43:09.000Z","msg":"其中蔡約翰、告東尼及大摩三大廐整次賽事合共出馬40匹，居然無一獲勝，至於雷神莫雷拉全日騎十駒，亦全軍盡墨，最高名次只是第四（包括第五場「精算風暴」及第九場「當家精選」），全日他單在獨贏、位置、連贏三大彩池，共輸掉近2億元投注額，難怪有網民叫佢做初三「瘟神」！  <br />\n<br />\n又累巴士佬俾人𨳒又累死人又累人輸錢，正一仆街冚家鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6608c0a32e9d8011b2f673d076f504630f4c25","tid":565194,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:44:28.000Z","msg":"累埋A09無錢叫雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬迷精彩語錄：<br />\n屌你老母隻當家精選真係仆街馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/564940/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/564940/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"42016c13d9cc0bb5d9dcb65d6cc3dc1ed74fd80a","tid":565194,"uid":1426,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:51:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/015136_001f19731eb17d3ad1a8aa5cf2d54fd0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F015136_001f19731eb17d3ad1a8aa5cf2d54fd0.png&h=35ac1583&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/015137_f1f58f332a758c5d7f74b60e04b93b99.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F015137_f1f58f332a758c5d7f74b60e04b93b99.png&h=b6d55ca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"7a85cc2fc5d6a2ed37019da6929d237024be2ca6","tid":565194,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:52:26.000Z","msg":"圖more"},{"pid":"bd1aa